---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Ascot | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Ascot. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Ascot and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:360px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(4).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 45%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.92) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.5) 55%,rgba(15,23,42,0.18) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Ascot</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,52px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plasterer in Ascot</h1>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">SL5 · Premium plastering &amp; decorating for Ascot's high-value residential properties.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">About Ascot</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">One of the most high-value residential areas in the service corridor. Large properties, premium finish expectations, consistent Venetian plastering demand.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Ascot carries an exceptionally high average property value — the racecourse, Royal connections, and proximity to Windsor attract a clientele with premium interior expectations. Large detached properties on substantial plots, many with high-specification interior renovations in progress at any given time.</p>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Venetian plastering, polished plaster in entrance halls and principal rooms, and sash window painting on period properties are the most frequent enquiries. Exterior render maintenance on rendered properties. We're at the south-western limit of the corridor — Ascot is typically covered on planned runs from Harefield via Windsor or Bracknell.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Common problems</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">What goes wrong in Ascot's housing stock.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Large render &amp; masonry elevations</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The big detached houses present substantial rendered and masonry elevations that weather over time and need quality patch repair and a premium paint system.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Matching existing polished plaster</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Where Venetian and polished plaster already exists in principal rooms, repair has to match the original sheen and texture exactly. There's no margin for an approximate patch.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Sash window upkeep</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The period properties carry original sash windows that need periodic strip, repair, and repainting to stay weathertight and looking right.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Neighbourhoods we work in</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Among the highest-value addresses in the corridor.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Ascot carries an exceptionally high average property value — the racecourse, Royal connections, and proximity to Windsor draw a clientele with premium interior expectations. Large detached properties sit on substantial plots around <strong>Sunninghill, Sunningdale, and the Ascot wards</strong>, with high-specification renovations a constant feature.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">It's a postcode where polished plaster in the entrance hall is the norm rather than the exception.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What homeowners ask for</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Venetian plaster and premium painting.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Venetian and polished plaster in halls and principal rooms is the most frequent enquiry, alongside premium exterior render and masonry painting, sash window work on the period stock, and high-end interior decorating. Exterior work is planned for dry conditions.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Discreet, exacting work — and a fixed price agreed before we start.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Ascot</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~45 minutes from base</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">At the south-western limit of the corridor, reached via the M25 and M4. Covered on planned runs through Windsor or Bracknell.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Premium finishes</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Venetian plaster and high-end paint systems applied to the standard the address calls for — the right materials, the right finish.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Discreet &amp; tidy</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Generous plots give ample access. We work cleanly and discreetly, features and surfaces fully protected.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Insured &amp; qualified</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Fully insured and City &amp; Guilds qualified. No subcontractors — the same person quotes and works.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:0;">
  <div style="position:relative;height:clamp(300px,42vw,440px);">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(6)%20.webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.78) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.18) 55%,rgba(15,23,42,0) 100%);"></div>
    <div style="position:relative;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:0 24px 40px;box-sizing:border-box;">
      <p style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,26px);font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;max-width:600px;margin:0;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.3;">Polished Venetian plaster, applied by hand to a flawless finish.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:48px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 18px;">Services in Ascot</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:10px;">
      <a href="/services/venetian-plastering" style="padding:14px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;" style-hover="background:#E0FAFF;border-color:#0C7BA8;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;">Venetian Plastering</span></a>
      <a href="/services/exterior-painting" style="padding:14px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;" style-hover="background:#E0FAFF;border-color:#0C7BA8;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;">Exterior Painting</span></a>
      <a href="/services/interior-painting" style="padding:14px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;" style-hover="background:#E0FAFF;border-color:#0C7BA8;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;">Interior Painting</span></a>
      <a href="/services/sash-window-painting" style="padding:14px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;" style-hover="background:#E0FAFF;border-color:#0C7BA8;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;">Sash Window Painting</span></a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:20px;"><p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#64748B;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 12px;">Nearby</p><div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;"><a href="/areas/windsor" style="padding:6px 13px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Windsor</a><a href="/areas/bracknell" style="padding:6px 13px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Bracknell</a><a href="/areas/binfield" style="padding:6px 13px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Binfield</a></div></div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,36px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get a quote for work in Ascot.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 28px;">Premium finishes. Fixed price. Based in Harefield.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;"><a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a><a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a></div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
